item.description:
Hey Folks, the weather prediction for this coming saturday is absolutely QQ friendly, especially for us who've been climbignthere since january ;-). Also, it turns out that the Boston Rock Climbing Meetup (of which some of you have dual membership) is planning a meetup at QQ, so the joint should be jumping, as it were. I predict many ropes up, many topropes a couple leads, video mongering, photos snapped, etc etc and so goes the battle.

bring your ropes, bring your selfs, just bring it, Yo!

Robb
item.how_to_find_us: the red jetta, the the camcorder, you all know the drill by now ;-)
